# Qversity v2 — Fintech/Banking Data Engineering Project

End-to-end ELT data pipeline for a fictional LATAM Fintech/Banking company. Ingests a raw JSON dataset from S3, transforms it through a Bronze/Silver/Gold lakehouse architecture, and exposes business insights via a PowerBI dashboard.

